import { Component } from '@angular/core'; import { Car } from './api/models'; import { Service } from './api/services'; @Component({ selector: 'app-root', templateUrl: './app.component.html', styleUrls: ['./app.component.css'] }) export class AppComponent { title = 'cars'; cars : Car[] =[]; constructor (private serv : Service){ } ngOnInit(): void { this.serv.getAllCar().subscribe((car) => { this.cars = car; }); } }
